  <entry>
    <title>pyecharts图像插入hexo中</title>
    <url>/2023/11/08/explore/pyecharts%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5hexo%E4%B8%AD/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p><strong>完成效果</strong><br>pyecharts渲染出的html作为元素插入到hexo中</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="实现方法"><a href="#实现方法" class="headerlink" title="实现方法"></a>实现方法</h3><h4 id="1-复制html到指定路径，设置hexo不渲染"><a href="#1-复制html到指定路径，设置hexo不渲染" class="headerlink" title="1. 复制html到指定路径，设置hexo不渲染"></a>1. 复制html到指定路径，设置hexo不渲染</h4><p>复制渲染出的html文件，例如RadarChart.html，在html文件最开始位置插入如下片段</p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Plaintext"><figure class="iseeu highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">layout: false</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p>不让hexo渲染该html文件</p>
<h4 id="2-采用iframe的方式插入"><a href="#2-采用iframe的方式插入" class="headerlink" title="2. 采用iframe的方式插入"></a>2. 采用iframe的方式插入</h4><p>需要设置RadarChart.html的文件路径，这里我们在source文件夹下新建一个appendix文件夹，添加RadarChart.html，在经过hexo生成后，会生成在public&#x2F;appendix目录下，设置好RadarChart.html的文件路径即可。</p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Html"><figure class="iseeu highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="keyword">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">http-equiv</span>=<span class="string">&quot;Content-Type&quot;</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">&quot;text/html; charset=UTF-8&quot;</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">iframe</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;../../../../../appendix/RadarChart.html&quot;</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">&quot;520px&quot;</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">&quot;100%&quot;</span> <span class="attr">scrolling</span>=<span class="string">&quot;yes&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">iframe</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<h5 id="效果展示"><a href="#效果展示" class="headerlink" title="效果展示"></a>效果展示</h5><!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/>
</head>
<body>
    <iframe src="../../../../../appendix/RadarChart.html" height="520px" width="100%" scrolling="yes">
    </iframe>
</body>

<p>不难发现，渲染后的图像无法自适应大小。可以在iframe外再设计一个div，来控制iframe的自定义缩放</p>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/>
</head>
<body>
<style>
        .box {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 540px;
            height: 340px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border: 1px solid black;
        }
</style>
<div class="box">
        <iframe 
            width="180%" 
            height="180%" 
            scrolling="yes"
            src="../../../../../appendix/RadarChart.html" 
            frameborder="0"
            scrolling="yes"
            style="transform: scale(0.6); position:absolute; left: -200px; top: -90px"
            >
        </iframe>
    </div>
</body>

<blockquote>
<p>div的大小为540*300，原图为900**500，设置比例为10:6</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>上面两种方法都存在bug，当页面存在侧边栏的时候，第一种会出现滚轮条，不便于查看，第二种会超出边界</p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
